<div class="text-25 text parbase section">

<p><strong>8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong>Privacy Policy</strong></p>


</div>

<div class="text parbase text-26 section">

<p>By using the Services, you indicate that you have reviewed and understand the information outlined in our Privacy Policy.&nbsp;</p>


